Bookdown

Builds on Rmarkdown

  • Numbering and cross-referencing
  • Footnotes
  • Literature references using bibtex
  • Knit multiple files to one document
    • All .Rmd files in director that do not start with "_"
    • Alt, specify .Rmd files in yaml
    • Use child documents

Bookdown (2)

  • Built-in formats
    • Gitbook
    • Tufte handout and html
  • Tools for making your own templates
